WEBVTT

00:02.423 --> 00:05.381
You've told me how little
you know about her.

00:05.383 --> 00:07.941
A Jew who lived through the war
in Europe.

00:07.943 --> 00:10.261
Who knows what lengths
she went to to survive?

00:10.263 --> 00:12.421
I don't care what it costs.

00:12.423 --> 00:15.101
Find something
that will rid us of her forever.

00:15.103 --> 00:16.661
You must not hurt our baby.

00:16.663 --> 00:18.461
It's taking a life, it's a sin.

00:18.463 --> 00:20.461
I couldn't be with you
if you did that, ever.

00:20.463 --> 00:22.621
The baby's gone.

00:22.623 --> 00:24.381
What if he doesn't believe me?

00:24.383 --> 00:26.141
He'll think
you've had an abortion?

00:26.143 --> 00:28.221
Can I kiss you?

00:28.223 --> 00:31.041
I'm gonna seek
professional help while I'm
there.

00:31.043 --> 00:32.741
There are doctors
for that sort of thing.

00:32.743 --> 00:35.821
I'll get it out of me,
even if he has to cut it out.

00:35.823 --> 00:38.403
What's it worth to you
for the world not to find out

00:38.448 --> 00:39.968
that your son's a queer?

00:40.928 --> 00:43.246
I reckon a thousand quid
should be about right.

00:43.248 --> 00:44.766
He's been seen
with Harry Polson!

00:44.768 --> 00:47.448
Oh, God.
We're being blackmailed!

00:47.473 --> 01:00.890
